    "body" : "<p>Maybe that:</p>\n\n<pre><code>   @Test\n    public void daysOfMonthTest() throws Exception {\n    Calendar mycal = new GregorianCalendar();\n\n    assertEquals(\n            31,\n            mycal.getActualMaximum(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH));\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
